Tekelec said it signed alicense agreement with British Telecommunications PLC &lt;BTY.L>to make and market a test instrument for digital microwavecommunications equipment.    Tekelec said the new product is expected to be priced at25,000 dlrs and to be shipped in the second half of 1987.    The 20-year, non-exclusive agreement grants Tekelec theright to manufacture and market the instrument in North Americaand Japan. Reuter&#3;